'''圣玛丽红崖教堂'''（{{lang-en|St. Mary Redcliffe}}）是一座圣公会[[教堂|教堂]]，位于[[英格兰|英格兰]][[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]。教堂建筑兴建于12-15世纪，是一座美丽的[[哥特式建筑|哥特式建筑]]，被英国遗产委员会列为一级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]<ref>{{Cite web | title=Church of St. Mary Redcliffe | work=Images of England | url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/details/default.aspx?id=380316 | accessdate=16 March 2007 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071208081913/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/details/default.aspx?id=380316 | archive-date=2007-12-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[伊丽莎白一世|伊丽莎白一世]]称之为“英格兰最均衡、最优美，也是最有名的教堂”<ref name="burrough">{{Cite book |last=Burrough |first=THB |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Bristol |year=1970 |publisher=Studio Vista |location=London |isbn=0-289-79804-3 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Little |first=Bryan |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=The City and County of Bristol |year=1967 |publisher=S. R. Publishers |location=Wakefield |isbn=0-85409-512-8 }}</ref>

圣玛丽红崖教堂是英国最大的[[堂区|牧区]]教堂<ref>{{Cite book|last1=Brackett|first1=Virginia|title=The Facts on File Companion to British Poetry: 17Th and 18th Centuries|date=2008|publisher=Infobase Publishing|page=67|accessdate=12 June 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last1=Ireland|first1=William Henry|title=Neglected genius, a poem|date=1812|publisher=W. Wilson|location=London|page=148|accessdate=12 June 2014}}</ref>，也是布里斯托尔的最高建筑。

